A pure Java interface to Scanii, a web based virus scanning engine (http://scanii.com) 

Requirements:
	1. Maven

Using it:
	1. Go to scanii.com and sign up for an API key 
	2. Once armed with your API key and secret, you can run by replacing KEY and SECRET with the proper
	information 
	3. Checkout the ScaniiClient class and unit test for example


Compiling:
    You can compile scanii-java.jar by running:

    $ mvn install -DskipTests
